%e A005820 120 = 2^3*3*5;  sigma(120) = (2^4-1)/1*(3^2-1)/2*(5^2-1)/4 = (15)*(4)*(6) = (3*5)*(2^2)*(2*3) = 2^3*3^2*5 = (3) * (2^3*3*5) = 3 * 120. - _Daniel Forgues_, May 09 2010
